cs.CL, cs.SI, cs.SD, cs.CY, cs.CR

This paper deals with natural language processing (NLP) techniques to identify depression and self-harm risk in online forums. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CL (Computation and Language), which deals with NLP and related topics. The paper also involves machine learning techniques, which could fall under cs.SI (Social and Information Networks) and cs.SD (Software Engineering). Additionally, the paper deals with mental health, which could fall under cs.CY (Computers and Society) and cs.CR (Cryptography and Security).
